body: anyways I had a dream that Ryan Reynolds was on some talk show and they showed him a video of dan and phil saying that they loved him and would really like to meet him. Then they asked Ryan who he thought those two guys were and he said “the dobre brothers?”. The show had dan and phil walk out on stage and Ryan asked if they were in fact the dobre brothers and that made phil cry. He started sobbing into dan’s shirt and dan was like wow Ryan look what you’ve done. Then I awoke.
